%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20couple%20spent%20hours%20near%20a%20passenger's%20body.%20Here's%20how%20cabin%20crew%20are%20trained%20to%20handle%20deaths%20in%20the%20air.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Boeing%20787-9%20Dreamliner%20from%20Qatar%20Airways%20is%20landing%20at%20Barcelona%20Airport%20in%20Barcelona%2C%20Spain%2C%20on%20February%2028%2C%202023%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65968b6a1c5c7b8c9a0dd256%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20passenger%20died%20on%20a%20recent%20Qatar%20Airways%20flight%20from%20Melbourne%20to%20Doha.%3Cp%3EUrbanandsport%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20couple%20said%20they%20had%20to%20share%20a%20row%20with%20a%20dead%20body%20after%20a%20passenger%20died%20on%20their%20flight.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20former%20flight%20attendant%20told%20BI%20how%20crew%20are%20trained%20to%20deal%20with%20medical%20emergencies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20airline%20trade%20organization%20has%20guidelines%20for%20dealing%20with%20deaths%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMitchell%20Ring%20and%20Jennifer%20Colin%20were%20heading%20to%20Venice%20when%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-airlines-passenger-dies-after-severe-turbulence-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassenger%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20their%20flight%20from%20Melbourne%20to%20Doha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERing%20told%20Australia's%20Nine%20News%20he%20spent%20the%20last%20four%20hours%20of%20the%2014-hour%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqatar-airways-qsuite-skytrax-best-business-class-review-airbus-a350-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQatar%20Airways%3C%2Fa%3E%20flight%20sharing%20a%20row%20with%20the%20woman's%20dead%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20passenger%20collapsed%20in%20the%20aisle%20near%20their%20row%2C%20Ring%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20did%20everything%20they%20could%2C%20but%20unfortunately%20the%20lady%20couldn't%20be%20saved%2C%20which%20was%20pretty%20heartbreaking%20to%20watch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20tried%20to%20wheel%20her%20up%20toward%20business%20class%2C%20but%20she%20was%20quite%20a%20large%20lady%20and%20they%20couldn't%20get%20her%20through%20the%20aisle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-quit-flight-attendant-job-after-5-years-unexpected-downsides-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflight%20attendants%3C%2Fa%3E%20saw%20there%20were%20two%20vacant%20seats%20in%20Ring%20and%20Colin's%20row%20of%20four.%20They%20then%20asked%20Ring%20to%20move%20over%20and%20placed%20the%20body%20in%20the%20seat%20where%20he%20had%20been%20sitting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERing%20said%20that%20the%20cabin%20crew%20didn't%20offer%20the%20couple%20different%20seats%20to%20move%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20another%20passenger%20in%20the%20row%20behind%20offered%20one%20to%20his%20wife%2C%20Ring%20told%20Nine%20News%20he%20spent%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20flight%20in%20the%20same%20row%20as%20the%20dead%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20was%20told%20to%20stay%20seated%20after%20the%20plane%20landed%2C%20as%20medical%20crews%20boarded%20the%20plane%20and%20removed%20blankets%20covering%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20thoughts%20are%20with%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20passenger%20who%20sadly%20passed%20away%20on%20board%20a%20recent%20Qatar%20Airways%20flight%20from%20Melbourne%2C%20Australia%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20airline%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20safety%20and%20comfort%20of%20all%20our%20passengers%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQatar%20said%20it%20had%20contacted%20the%20affected%20passengers%20to%20address%20their%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeaths%20on%20airplanes%20are%20not%20unheard%20of%2C%20though%20they%20are%20comparatively%20rare.%20A%202013%20study%20found%20that%20medical%20emergencies%20happen%20once%20in%20every%20604%20flights.%20Deaths%20are%20even%20rarer%2C%20resulting%20from%200.3%25%20of%20such%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214cfff44-245b-41c7-854d-de0f6743fd84%5C%22%3EHow%20crew%20are%20trained%20to%20deal%20with%20dead%20passengers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20economy%20cabin%20with%20red%20screens%20on%20Iberia's%20A321XLR.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673b6fc5ede4eeae39282eb7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPassengers%20who%20die%20during%20flights%20are%20often%20placed%20in%20an%20empty%20row%20of%20seats.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20actually%20happens%20when%20someone%20dies%20on%20a%20plane%3F%20Airlines%20have%20protocols%20in%20place%2C%20and%20staff%20are%20trained%20to%20deal%20with%20medical%20emergencies.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2024-to-break-records-for-air-travel-and-airline-profits-iata-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Air%20Transport%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20airline%20trade%20group%2C%20has%20guidelines%20for%20dealing%20with%20a%20death%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20told%20to%20be%20as%20compassionate%20and%20understanding%20as%20possible%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20passenger%20was%20traveling%20with%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Pierre-Yves%20Monnerville%2C%20who%20spent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-attendant-unruly-drunk-passengers-rude-colleagues-harder-to-handle-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E17%20years%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20carriers%20including%20British%20Airways%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIdeally%2C%20he%20said%2C%20there%20would%20be%20an%20empty%20row%20to%20place%20the%20body.%20In%20the%20Qatar%20Airways%20case%2C%20Monnerville%20said%20he%20suspected%20that%20the%20flight%20would've%20been%20very%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20was%20trained%20to%20%26quot%3Bfind%20a%20way%20to%20make%20them%20as%20inconspicuous%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%20For%20example%2C%20not%20putting%20a%20blanket%20over%20their%20head%20and%20keeping%20them%20upright%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Monnerville%20didn't%20deal%20with%20a%20passenger's%20death%20during%20his%20time%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%2C%20he%20said%20he%20used%20to%20do%20first%20aid%20with%20the%20French%20Red%20Cross%20%E2%80%94%20where%20he%20experienced%20how%20difficult%20it%20can%20be%20to%20move%20a%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomebody%20unconscious%20already%20is%20quite%20hard%20to%20deal%20with%20in%20a%20regular%20house%2C%20but%20you%20can%20imagine%20in%20such%20a%20confined%20space%20%5Bas%20a%20plane%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonnerville%20added%20that%20it%20would%20be%20an%20extra%20challenge%20on%20newer%20planes%20as%20the%20aisles%20are%20narrower%20to%20fit%20in%20more%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQatar%20Airways%20said%20in%20a%20Friday%20statement%20shared%20with%20BBC%20News%20that%20the%20crew's%20handling%20of%20the%20woman's%20death%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20line%20with%20training%20and%20industry%20standard%20practice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20went%20viral%20on%20TikTok%20as%20she%20explained%20procedures%20if%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeath-on-plane-what-happens-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassenger%20dies%20on%20a%20plane%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20have%20a%20heart%20attack%20and%20die%2C%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20we%20can%20do%20about%20it%2C%20and%20we%20can't%20start%20CPR%2C%20we%20are%20just%20going%20to%20wait%20until%20we%20get%20to%20our%20final%20destination%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheena%20Marie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%2C%20despite%20a%20myth%20of%20bodies%20being%20put%20in%20airplane%20bathrooms%2C%20this%20isn't%20possible%20as%20a%20body%20can't%20be%20safely%20strapped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20some%20planes%20even%20had%20specific%20compartments%20reserved%20for%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-new-business-class-game-changer-long-haul-flying-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESingapore%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20operating%20Airbus%20A340-500s%20with%20a%20locker%20that%20could%20store%20a%20body%2C%20which%20became%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcorpse%20cupboard.%26quot%3B%20The%20airline%20retired%20its%20A340-500s%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221799%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Airbus%20A350-941%20from%20Singapore%20Airlines%20is%20taking%20off%20from%20Barcelona%20Airport%20in%20Barcelona%2C%20Spain%2C%20on%20February%2029%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662f810c10dfcda409644ab9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221225%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Singapore%20Airlines%20Airbus%20A350.%20The%20carrier%20previously%20operated%20%26quot%3Bcorpse%20cupboards%26quot%3B%20on%20some%20planes.%3Cp%3EUrbanandsport%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20IATA's%20more%20formal%20guidelines%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20flight%20crews%20should%20do%20is%20notify%20the%20captain%2C%20who%20should%20then%20inform%20authorities%20at%20the%20destination%20airport.%20The%20deceased%20should%20then%20be%20moved%20to%20a%20seat%20with%20few%20passengers%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20flight%20is%20full%2C%20the%20b