ince%20Trump%20was%20elected%20the%20US%20president.%20The%20spate%20of%20tariff%20announcements%20by%20Trump%20has%20been%20impacting%20markets%20and%20the%20latest%20announcement%20of%20additional%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20China%20is%20a%20confirmation%20of%20the%20market%20view%20that%20Trump%20will%20use%20the%20initial%20months%20of%20his%20presidency%20to%20threaten%20countries%20with%20tariffs%20and%20then%20negotiate%20for%20a%20settlement%20favourable%20to%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20VK%20Vijayakumar%2C%20Chief%20Investment%20Strategist%2C%20Geojit%20Financial%20Services%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20China%20responds%20to%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20tariffs%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20the%2025%25%20duties%20on%20imports%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20would%20come%20into%20effect%20on%20March%204%2C%20the%20day%20the%20month-long%20pause%20ends%2C%20and%20not%20April%202%20as%20he%20had%20hinted%20at%20earlier.%20%26quot%3BChina%20will%20likewise%20be%20charged%20an%20additional%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20that%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20Chinese%20imports%20will%20be%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20levy%20at%20the%20same%20rate%20that%20the%20US%20president%20had%20imposed%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20on%20Friday%20said%20it%20would%20to%20take%20%26quot%3Ball%20necessary%20countermeasures%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20impose%20the%20additional%20tariff%20would%20%26quot%3Bseriously%20impact%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740739740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fv7agfveg_sensex_625x300_27_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsensex-plunges-1-400-points-to-settle-at-73-198-10-nifty-tanks-420-points-to-22-124-7815520%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sensex%20plunged%20over%201%2C400%20points%20while%20the%20Nifty%20tanked%20420%20points%20in%20line%20with%20global%20markets%2C%20which%20have%20been%20rattled%20by%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20announcement%20of%20an%20additional%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Nitish%20And%20BJP%3A%20Will%20Bihar%20See%20A%20Maharashtra%20'Rerun'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Bihar%20assembly%20elections%20due%20in%20October%20or%20November%20this%20year%2C%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20in%20the%20state%20has%20expanded%20its%20cabinet%20to%20fill%20vacant%20positions.%20The%20appointments%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20are%20aimed%20at%20balancing%20caste%20and%20regional%20aspirations%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20boost%20the%20alliance's%20prospects.%20While%20all%20the%20seven%20ministers%20belong%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20highlighting%20its%20heft%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20a%20big%20question%20mark%20hangs%20over%20whether%20the%20party%20will%20contest%20the%20polls%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20its%20chief%20ministerial%20face%2C%20or%20whether%20it%20pull%20an%20Eknath%20Shinde%20post-poll.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAge%20And%20Health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Nitish's%20waning%20health%20and%20popularity%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20insists%20on%20naming%20him%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate.%20Given%20the%20contentious%20issue%20of%20ticket%20distribution%20and%20Nitish's%20tendency%20to%20jump%20ships%2C%20the%20next%20few%20months%20could%20set%20off%20a%20political%20potboiler%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20cabinet%20expansion%20has%20also%20led%20to%20rumours%20that%20the%20state%20elections%20could%20be%20pre-poned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20BJP%20ministers%20sworn%20in%20are%20Sanjay%20Saraogi%20(Darbhanga)%2C%20Sunil%20Kumar%20(Biharsharif)%2C%20Jibesh%20Kumar%20(Jale)%2C%20Raju%20Kumar%20Singh%20(Sahebganj)%2C%20Moti%20Lal%20Prasad%20(Riga)%2C%20Krishna%20Kumar%20Mantu%20(Amnour)%20and%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Mandal%20(Sikti).%20Out%20of%20these%20seven%20leaders%2C%20four%20belong%20to%20the%20OBC%20community%2C%20one%20to%20the%20EBC%2C%20and%20two%20are%20from%20upper%20castes%2C%20the%20core%20voting%20segments%20of%20the%20saffron%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strength%20of%20the%20Cabinet%20goes%20up%20to%2037%20with%20this%20expansion%3B%20this%20includes%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%2022%20leaders%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%2013%20from%20the%20JD(U)%2C%20one%20from%20the%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20(HAM)%2C%20and%20one%20Independent.%20This%20is%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20total%20strength%20of%20alliance%20parties%20in%20the%20House%3A%2084%20members%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%2048%20from%20the%20JD(U).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20Calculations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost-expansion%2C%20Nitish's%20Cabinet%20now%20has%2028%25%20representation%20from%20the%20OBC%20community%20and%2019%25%20from%20the%20SCs.%20This%20is%20broadly%20in%20line%20with%20the%20population%20share%20of%20the%20two%20groups.%20However%2C%20the%20representation%20of%20Economically%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBC)%20and%20Most%20Backward%20Classes%20(MBC)%20is%20still%20low%3A%20just%2019%25%2C%20when%20they%20make%20up%2036%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%20This%20is%20mostly%20because%20around%2011%25%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%20are%20classified%20as%20EBC%2FMBC%2C%20while%20there%20is%20just%20one%20Muslim%20minister%20from%20the%20community%20in%20the%20entire%20Cabinet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20General%20category%20leaders%20make%20up%2031%25%20of%20the%20Cabinet%2C%20which%20is%20twice%20their%20population.%20Four%20ministers%20are%20from%20the%2015-seat%20Greater%20Mithilanchal%20region.%20The%20NDA%20had%20won%2097%20of%20these%20in%202020%2C%20and%20the%20latest%20appointment%20is%20aimed%20at%20consolidating%20its%20base%20further%20in%20this%20zone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20both%20alliances%20had%20fetched%20around%2037%25%20of%20votes.%20However%2C%20the%20NDA%20received%2011%2C150%20votes%20more%20than%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)-led%20Mahagathbandhan.%20It%20bagged%20125%20of%20the%20243%20seats%2C%20three%20more%20than%20the%20simple%20majority%2C%20and%20ended%20up%20forming%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECentral%20Considerations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20as%20well%2C%20Bihar%20is%20expected%20to%20see%20a%20tight%20election.%20The%20key%20question%20before%20the%20BJP%20is%20whether%20it%20will%20declare%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20face%20of%20the%20alliance.%20If%20it%20pulls%20a%20Maharashtra%20in%20Bihar%20and%20decides%20on%20a%20name%20after%20the%20results%2C%20the%20post%20could%20then%20go%20to%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20depending%20upon%20their%20performance%20in%20the%20election.%20This%20is%20crucial%20because%20before%20going%20to%20the%20polls%20in%202020%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20declared%20that%20Nitish%20would%20be%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20parties'%20seat%20tally%20in%20the%20election.%20The%20BJP%20honoured%20its%20promise%20despite%20getting%20almost%20twice%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20than%20the%20JD(U).%20A%20section%20of%20the%20parties'%20cadre%20and%20supporters%20didn't%20appreciate%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nitish%20made%20a%20%3Cem%3Egharwapsi%20%3C%2Fem%3Ejust%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20election%2C%20he%20was%20still%20retained%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20the%20BJP%2C%20falling%20short%20of%20a%20majority%2C%20needed%20the%20support%20of%20the%20JDU's%2012%20MLAs%20in%20Parliament.%20Nitish%20may%20use%20this%20as%20a%20bargaining%20chip%20in%20the%20upcoming%20state%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JD(U)%2C%20already%20jittery%20after%20the%20BJP's%20Maharashtra%20move%2C%20has%20been%20demanding%20that%20the%20NDA%20announce%20Nitish%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20immediately.%20Any%20delay%20can%20complicate%20matters%2C%20given%20the%20buzz%20about%20the%2074-year-old%20leader's%20deteriorating%20health.%20Further%2C%20the%20clamour%20in%20the%20party%20to%20name%20Nitish's%20son%2C%20Nishant%2C%20as%20his%20successor%2C%20is%20only%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20parties%20in%20India%20are%20mostly%20family-controlled.%20Already%2C%20questions%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20the%20JD(U)'s%20future%20after%20Nitish%2C%20who%20commands%20as%20much%20as%2012-15%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20thanks%20to%20the%20Kurmi%2C%20EBC%2FMBC%20and%20Mahadalit%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatchwork%20Politics%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20a%20BJP%20do%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20on%20the%20JD(U)%20just%20before%20the%20polls%2C%20forcing%20a%20leadership%20change%20and%20installing%20a%20BJP%20Chief%20Minister%3F%20RJD%20supremo%20Lalu%20Yadav%20has%20already%20been%20making%20overtures%20to%20Nitish%20to%20join%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%2C%20though%20the%20latter%20has%20publicly%20declined%20the%20offer.%20With%20just%20six%20months%20to%20go%20before%20the%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20want%20to%20avoid%20such%20patchwork%20politics%20and%20play%20its%20cards%20after%20the%20election%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeat%20distribution%20talks%20with%20the%20JD(U)%20are%20also%20going%20to%20be%20tricky.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20party%20contested%20115%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20fought%20for%20110%2C%20the%20Vikassheel%20Insaan%20Party%20(VIP)%20for%2011%2C%20and%20the%20HAM%20for%20seven.%20However%2C%20this%20time%2C%20there's%20one%20more%20element%20to%20the%20mix%3A%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP).%20Citing%20its%20current%20strength%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20want%20to%20contest%20on%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20seats%20than%20the%20JD(U).%20But%20Nitish%20is%20unlikely%20to%20budge%20on%20this%20as%20it%20would%20directly%20affect%20his%20prospects%20at%20the%20post-poll%20negotiating%20table.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'PK'%20Factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20slew%20of%20moving%20parts%20will%20define%20this%20year's%20Bihar%20election.%20There%20is%20also%20the%20%E2%80%98PK'%20or%20Prashant%20Kishor%20factor.%20While%2015%25%20of%20voters%20want%20to%20see%20him%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20his%20Jan%20Suraaj%20party%20got%2010%25%20votes%20in%20the%20by-polls%20held%20last%20year.%20Which%20way%20would%20'PK'%20strike%3F%20The%20Muslim-Yadav%20vote%20bank%20of%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%2C%20or%20the%20upper%20caste%20and%20OBC%2FEBC%20base%20of%20the%20NDA%3F%20The%20answer%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20is%20blowin'%20in%20the%20wind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740739440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F7ioepi98_narendra-modi-nitish-kumar_625x300_07_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnitish-and-bjp-will-bihar-see-a-maharashtra-rerun-7814915%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20all%20the%20seven%20ministers%20belong%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20highlighting%20its%20heft%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20a%20big%20question%20mark%20hangs%20over%20whether%20the%20party%20will%20contest%20the%20polls%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20its%20CM%20face%2C%20or%20whether%20it%20pull%20an%20'Eknath%20Shinde'%20post-poll.