nce%2C%20and%20figuring%20out%20why%20there's%20a%20half-eaten%20granola%20bar%20stuck%20to%20the%20upholstery.%20I%20knew%20how%20to%20change%20a%20diaper.%20But%20nothing%20prepared%20me%20for%20the%20sheer%20volume%20of%20diapers%20a%20tiny%20human%20can%20produce%20in%20just%20one%20day.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228788a567-4b06-4817-abab-6f4ec6606def%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20myth%20of%20control%20I%20had%20as%20an%20aunt%20busted%20when%20I%20became%20a%20mother%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20used%20to%20laugh%20when%20people%20said%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-happens-when-you-dont-get-enough-sleep-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esleep%20deprivation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20torture.%20Now%2C%20I%20understand.%20I've%20negotiated%20with%20a%202-year-old%20over%20pajama%20colors%20at%203%20a.m.%2C%20and%20I've%20lost%20arguments%20with%20a%204-year-old%20about%20whether%20only%20ketchup%20on%20toast%20qualifies%20as%20breakfast.%20I've%20learned%20that%20%26quot%3Bmommy%20brain%26quot%3B%20is%20real%2C%20my%20tolerance%20for%20noise%20is%20superhuman%2C%20and%20I%20can%20function%20on%20minimal%20sleep.%20None%20of%20which%2C%20I'll%20now%20admit%2C%20I%20ever%20had%20to%20endure%20as%20an%20aunt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20babysat%20my%20nieces%20and%20nephews%2C%20all%20I%20cared%20about%20was%20being%20the%20fun%20aunt.%20There%20was%20no%20pressure%20to%20parent%20the%20right%20way.%20I%20made%20their%20favorite%20snacks%2C%20curated%20their%20YouTube%20playlists%2C%20dressed%20them%20up%20in%20adorable%20outfits%2C%20and%20styled%20their%20hair.%20The%20stakes%20were%20low%2C%20and%20the%20joy%20was%20abundant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2203e51404-286e-42b6-9e6f-010c7d50dcb1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20why%2C%20after%20babysitting%20for%20years%2C%20was%