ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn527pz54neo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shubman%20Gill%20To%20Captain%20India%20vs%20NZ%3F%20Report%20Makes%20Big%20Rohit%20Sharma%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20might%20just%20get%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20future%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand%2C%20with%20vice-captain%20Shubman%20Gill%20likely%20to%20be%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20captain%20the%20team.%20With%20Rohit%20Sharma%20not%20hundred%20percent%20from%20fitness%20point%20of%20view%2C%20a%20report%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20team%20management%20could%20decide%20to%20rest%20the%20skipper%20for%20the%20team's%20final%20Group%20A%20game%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20Since%20India's%20progression%20to%20the%20semi-finals%20is%20already%20sealed%2C%20the%20management%20can%20afford%20to%20rest%20Rohit%20for%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Rohit%20is%20indeed%20rested%2C%20vice-captain%20Shubman%20Gill%20is%20expected%20to%20lead%20the%20team.%20Gill%20has%20been%20backed%20by%20many%20to%20become%20India's%20captain%2C%20maybe%20even%20across%20formats%2C%20in%20the%20future.%20The%20cricketing%20fraternity%2C%20hence%2C%20might%20be%20able%20to%20take%20a%20sneak-peak%20into%20the%20future%2C%20understanding%20what%20sort%20of%20leadership%20skills%20Gill%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fchampions-trophy-rohit-sharma-hamstring-injury-rest-india-vs-new-zealand-9858575%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rohit%20is%20still%20struggling%20with%20a%20hamstring%20issue%2C%20he%20had%20sustained%20during%20the%20last%20match%20against%20Pakistan.%20He%20even%20walked%20off%20the%20field%20in%20the%20match%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20Gill%20to%20lead%20the%20side.%20However%2C%20the%20Hitman%20later%20returned%20to%20take%20the%20baton%20in%20his%20own%20hands%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20however%2C%20Rohit%20didn't%20hit%20the%20nets.%20He%20was%20the%20only%20Indian%20batter%20to%20give%20the%20training%20session%20a%20miss.%20The%20batter%20didn't%20even%20take%20throwdowns.%20He%20was%20spotted%20working%20with%20India's%20strength%20and%20conditioning%20coach%20and%20physiotherapist%20indoors%2C%20fuelling%20speculation%20that%20all%20is%20not%20well%20with%20respect%20to%20his%20hamstring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Rohit%20is%20rested%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20changes%20in%20the%20batting%20position%20of%20the%20unit%20could%20be%20seen%20for%20the%20New%20Zealand%20clash.%20Rohit's%20absence%20could%20force%20KL%20Rahul%20to%20open%20with%20Shubman%20Gill%20at%20the%20top.%20Such%20a%20change%20could%20see%20Rishabh%20Pant%20being%20drafted%20into%20the%20team%2C%20taking%20up%20the%20finisher's%20role%20from%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20Pant%20takes%20up%20the%20wicket-keeper's%20role%20too%2C%20Rahul%20would%20need%20to%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20outfield%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20has%20been%20keeping%20wickets%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740738480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fo8hns5q_shubman-gill-and-rohit-sharma-afp_625x300_28_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fshubman-gill-to-captain-india-against-new-zealand-big-rohit-sharma-development-in-champions-trophy-7812849%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shubman%20Gill%20could%20make%20his%20India%20captaincy%20bow%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20for%20the%20final%20Group%20A%20game%20against%20New%20Zealand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fshubman-gill-to-captain-india-against-new-zealand-big-rohit-sharma-development-in-champions-trophy-7812849%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2241%20Workers%20Missing%20After%20Massive%20Avalanche%20Near%20Badrinath%2C%2016%20Rescued%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2041%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20(BRO)%20workers%20are%20trapped%20under%20an%20avalanche%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Chamoli%20district%2C%20officials%20said%20today.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20near%20the%20border%20village%20of%20Mana%2C%20about%20five%20kilometres%20from%20the%20Badrinath%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20total%20of%2057%20workers%20of%20which%2016%20have%20been%20so%20far%20rescued%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20army%20camp%20near%20Mana%20village%20in%20critical%20condition%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20first%20images%20of%20the%20rescue%20operation%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndianArmy%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23IndianArmy%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSuryaCommand%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SuryaCommand%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAn%20avalanche%20struck%20a%20GREF%20Camp%20near%20Mana%20village%20in%20Garhwal%20Sector.%20A%20number%20of%20labourers%20are%20feared%20to%20be%20trapped.%20Indian%20Army's%20IBEX%20BRIGADE%20swiftly%20launched%20rescue%20operations%20inspite%20of%20continuing%20heavy%20snowfall%20and%20minor%20avalanches.%20So%20far%2010%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FadVcAu9g4g%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FadVcAu9g4g%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20SuryaCommand_IA%20(%40suryacommand)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuryacommand%2Fstatus%2F1895403906148245569%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2028%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5C