rents-ceos-make-counselor-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20former%20top%20Biden%20DEI%20chief%20says%20companies%20should%20'bunker%20down'%20and%20stand%20up%20for%20diversity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20portrait%20of%20Dr%20Alaysia%20Black%20Hackett%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a36fc4bfebcc4d029dcfbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr%20Alaysia%20Black%20Hackett%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dr%20Alaysia%20Black%20Hackett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20Biden's%20top%20DEI%20chiefs%20said%20she%20wants%20to%20dispel%20%26quot%3Bmyths%26quot%3B%20amid%20Trump's%20rollback%20of%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAlaysia%20Black%20Hackett%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20corporations%20should%20hold%20firm%20to%20DEI%20practices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20that%20companies%20are%20now%20reaching%20out%20to%20her%20for%20advice.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20DEI%20chief%20who%20served%20in%20the%20Biden%20administration%20wants%20to%20%26quot%3Bdispel%20a%20lot%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20myths%26quot%3B%20swirling%20around%20diversity%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20the%20idea%20that%20DEI%20hires%20aren't%20recruited%20on%20merit%2C%20or%20that%20diversity%20initiatives%20are%20only%20aimed%20at%20benefiting%20Black%20People%2C%20said%20Alaysia%20Black%20Hackett%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Department%20of%20Labor's%20chief%20diversity%20and%20equity%20officer%20before%20resigning%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%3A%20'You%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20have%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20leadership%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20Black%20Hackett%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20data%20to%20say%3A%20'What%20groups%20of%20people%20are%20we%20missing%20and%20how%20can%20this%20be%20a%20detriment%20to%20the%20service%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sentiment%20toward%20DEI%20has%20been%20shifting%20in%20recent%20months.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2024%2F11%2F19%2Fviews-of-dei-have-become-slightly-more-negative-among-us-workers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20people%20who%20see%20DEI%20as%20a%20positive%20fell%20from%2056%25%20to%2052%25%20between%20February%202023%20and%20October%202024.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20those%20who%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20bad%20thing%20grew%20from%2016%25%20to%2021%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Black%20Hackett%20says%20the%20field%20is%20misunderstood%2C%20in%20part%20thanks%20to%20a%20tough%20media%20environment%2C%20and%20the%20Biden%20administration%20not%20being%20good%20at%20touting%20its%20own%20achievements.%20She%20said%20she%20believes%20people%20don't%20want%20to%20understand%20what%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20inclusion%2C%20and%20accessibility%20really%20stand%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20to%20hate%20it%20because%20it%20seemed%20to%20benefit%20one%20race%20of%20people%20more%20than%20it%20fits%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc24a1dc-8875-476c-9ae8-ee3925623691%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20DEI%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20in%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20Black%20Hackett%20said%20federal%20hiring%20initiatives%20were%20merit-based%20and%20designed%20to%20%26quot%3Bensure%20that%20our%20internal%20federal%20workforce%20mirrored%20the%20communities%20that%20we%20serve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20federal%20bodies%20lacked%20diversity%20of%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20going%20to%20miss%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlack%20Hackett%20described%20much%20of%20her%20work%20as%20being%20aimed%20at%20making%20sure%20that%20federal%20funding%20filtered%20through%20to%20people%20who%20are%20either%20under-resourced%2C%20or%20are%20in%20historically%20underrepresented%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20her%20work%20focused%20on%20determining%20how%20federal%20funding%20could%20effectively%20reach%20marginalized%20communities.%20This%20included%20identifying%20rural%20communities%20that%20needed%20better%20internet%20access%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fixture%20in%20Biden's%20infrastructure%20law%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20data%20about%20rural%20communities%2C%20you%20will%20see%20that%20it's%20not%20typically%20inundated%20with%20people%20of%20color%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bmost%20Americans%20fit%20under%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20categories%20under%20DEIA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d9330b5b-a4a9-4677-946c-1b0405c18e47%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20corporate%20DEI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20last%20month%20ending%20DEI%20programs%20in%20the%20federal%20government.%20The%20Trump%20administration%20has%20said%20DEI%20%26quot%3Bdivided%20Americans%20by%20race%2C%20wasted%20taxpayer%20dollars%2C%20and%20resulted%20in%20shameful%20discrimination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20directed%20federal%20agencies%20to%20compile%20lists%20of%20private%20companies'%20DEI%20efforts%2C%20and%20many%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-cutting-dei-activist-backlash-harley-davidson-deere-tractor-supply-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20and%20Walmart%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20decided%20to%20roll%20back%20or%20end%20their%20DEI%20programs.%20Others%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-doubles-down-jpmorgan-diversity-efforts-dei-shareholder-activists-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJP%20Morgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-shareholders-reject-anti-dei-proposal-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECostco%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20not%20altered%20course%20on%20their%20diversity%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlack%20Hackett%20said%20that%20companies%20are%20reaching%20out%20to%20her%20for%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20small%20business%20owners%20who%20are%20asking%20me%3A%20'Alaysia%2C%20what%20do%20I%20do%3F%20What%20direction%20is%20this%20going%20to%20impact%20me%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20companies%20feeling%20cowed%20should%20%26quot%3Bbunker%20down%2C%20stand%20up%20for%20what's%20right%2C%20and%20look%20at%20your%20data%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20the%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProductivity%20goes%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BStatistics%20show%20that.%20People%20are%20more%20productive%20if%20they%20feel%20like%20they're%20welcome%20in%20their%20environment%2C%20their%20thoughts%2C%20their%20opinions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilo.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fwcmsp5%2Fgroups%2Fpublic%2F%2540ed_dialogue%2F%2540act_emp%2Fdocuments%2Fpublication%2Fwcms_841348.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20report%20by%20the%20International%20Labor%20Organization%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20DEI%20can%20add%20value%20to%20businesses%20through%20increased%20employee%20productivity%2C%20stronger%20collaboration%20with%20colleagues%2C%20and%20improved%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20DEI%20rollback%20could%20make%20people%20become%20%26quot%3Bafraid%20to%20even%20show%20up%20as%20their%20authentic%20selves%2C%26quot%3B%20Black%20Hackett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20she%20feels%20positive%20about%20the%20future%20of%20DEI%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20will%20say%2C%20and%20I%20will%20say%20it%20qu