AAP%20MLAs%2C%20including%20Atishi%2C%20were%20suspended%20for%20disrupting%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena's%20inaugural%20address%20by%20raising%20slogans%20against%20the%20alleged%20removal%20of%20portraits%20of%20BR%20Ambedkar%20and%20Bhagat%20Singh%20from%20Chief%20Minister%20Rekha%20Gupta's%20office%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20has%20an%20issue%20with%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20photo%20and%20his%20name.%20When%20we%20raised%20the%20'Jai%20Bheem'%20slogans%20inside%20the%20House%2C%20we%20were%20marshalled%20out%2C%20but%20when%20they%20raised%20'Modi%2C%20Modi'%20slogans%2C%20they%20were%20not%20marshalled%20out.%20Does%20this%20mean%20that%20the%20BJP%20think%20that%20PM%20Modi%20is%20bigger%20than%20BR%20Ambedkar%3F%26quot%3B%20Atishi%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20strongly%20worded%20letter%20to%20Delhi%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Vijender%20Gupta%2C%20Atishi%20called%20the%20suspension%20of%2021%20AAP%20MLAs%20an%20%26quot%3Binjustice%20to%20the%20opposition%26quot%3B%20and%20urged%20the%20Speaker%20to%20uphold%20democratic%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20writing%20this%20letter%20with%20great%20pain%20and%20sorrow.%20The%20biggest%20strength%20of%20democracy%20is%20its%20fairness%20and%20equality.%20But%20whatever%20happened%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20in%20the%20past%20few%20days%20is%20not%20only%20an%20injustice%20to%20the%20opposition%20MLAs%20but%20also%20a%20severe%20blow%20to%20democratic%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20Atishi's%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%20further%20alleged%20that%20disciplinary%20actions%20were%20selectively%20imposed%2C%20targeting%20opposition%20legislators%20while%20sparing%20those%20from%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%2025%20February%202025%2C%20during%20the%20address%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20MLAs%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20raised%20slogans%20of%20'Modi-Modi%2C'%20while%20the%20opposition%20MLAs%20raised%20slogans%20of%20'Jai%20Bheem%2C'%20respecting%20the%20views%20of%20Baba%20Saheb%20Dr.%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar.%20It%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20that%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20against%20any%20MLA%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20but%2021%20MLAs%20of%20the%20opposition%20were%20suspended%20from%20the%20House%20for%20three%20days%20for%20raising%20the%20slogan%20'Jai%20Bheem%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20deepened%20when%20the%20suspended%20AAP%20MLAs%20attempted%20to%20stage%20a%20protest%20near%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20statue%20within%20the%20Assembly%20premises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20injustice%20did%20not%20stop%20here.%20Yesterday%2C%20when%20the%20suspended%20MLAs%20were%20going%20to%20protest%20peacefully%20in%20front%20of%20the%20statue%20of%20Gandhiji%20present%20in%20the%20Assembly%20premises%2C%20they%20were%20stopped%20200%20meters%20before%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20Assembly%20and%20were%20prevented%20from%20entering%20the%20premises%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20called%20the%20restriction%20an%20%26quot%3Binsult%26quot%3B%20to%20both%20the%20MLAs%20and%20the%20public%20mandate%20they%20represent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20escalating%20political%20standoff%2C%20AAP%20MLAs%20announced%20their%20decision%20to%20take%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%20The%20party%20leadership%20sees%20the%20suspensions%20and%20restrictions%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20suppress%20opposition%20voices%20within%20the%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20the%20guardian%20of%20this%20Assembly.%20It%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20guardian%20to%20do%20equal%20justice%20to%20all%20the%20MLAs%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%20or%20the%20opposition.%20I%20urge%20you%20to%20protect%20the%20democratic%20values%20and%20ensure%20that%20no%20MLA%20is%20deprived%20of%20his%20constitutional%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20Atishi%20wrote%20in%20her%20letter%