ually%20there's%20nothing%20too%20crazy%20about%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Hart%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20start%20getting%20into%20houses%20that%20were%20built%20in%20the%201900s%20or%20earlier%2C%20which%20you%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20closer%20to%20downtown%20in%20West%20Louisville%2C%20who%20knows%20what's%20happened%20to%20that%20house%20over%20the%20past%20100%20years%3F%20You%20just%20encounter%20a%20lot%20of%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20business%20partners%20also%20wholesale%20real%20estate%20and%20buy%20and%20hold%20long-term%20rentals.%20In%202024%2C%20they%20did%2050%20transactions%20between%20wholesales%2C%20wholetails%2C%20and%20flips%2C%20and%20they%20own%20more%20than%2020%20rental%20properties%20throughout%20the%20Lousiville%20area.%20BI%20verified%20their%20property%20ownership%20and%20deal%20history%20by%20looking%20at%20settlement%20statements%20and%20closing%20documents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20like%20their%20market%20for%20a%20few%20different%20reasons.%20Hart%2C%20who%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Louisville%2C%20knows%20the%20city%20intimately.%20But%20Gorius%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Massachusetts%20and%20spent%20years%20living%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20chose%20to%20invest%20in%20Kentucky's%20largest%20city%20from%20afar.%20He's%20relocating%20to%20Louisville%20now%20that%20their%20real%20estate%20company%20has%20taken%20off%20and%20they%20have%20three%20employees%20to%20manage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGorius%2C%20whose%20first%20deal%20was%20a%20duplex%20that%20he%20turned%20into%20a%20long-term%20rental%2C%20looked%20at%20a%20few%20key%20factors%20when%20considering%20markets%20to%20invest%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Affordability.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20reason%20he%20didn't%20invest%20in%20the%20market%20he%20was%20living%20in%2C%20Phoenix%2C%20was%20because%20of%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nar.realtor%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2025-02%2Fmetro-home-prices-q4-2024-single-family-2025-02-06.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emedian%20sales%20price%20of%20existing%20single-family%20homes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20Phoenix%20metro%20area%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202024%20was%20%24476%2C400.%20In%20Louisville%2C%20it%20was%20%24279%2C200.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Presence%20of%20major%20companies.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20hub%20for%20UPS.%20Ford%20also%20has%20a%20plant%20there%20%E2%80%94%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20was%20looking%2C%20they%20had%20just%20announced%20that%20they%20were%20going%20to%20add%20a%20second%20plant%20there%20and%20that's%20still%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20built%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20these%20massive%2C%20massive%20companies%20are%20willing%20to%20invest%20in%20this%20city%20then%20it's%20definitely%20good%20enough%20for%20little%20old%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Vibe%20of%20the%20city.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EVisiting%20the%20area%20sealed%20the%20deal%20for%20Gorius%2C%20who%20enjoyed%20the%20mild%20weather%20and%20general%20vibe%3A%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20was%20super%2C%20super%20nice%2C%20just%20kind%20and%20saying%20hello%20and%20everyone%20was%20willing%20to%20help%20out.%20That's%20what%20drew%20me%20to%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHart%20weighed%20in%20on%20what%20he%20likes%20specifically%20about%20his%20native%20city.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20four%20seasons%20but%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20natural%20disasters%20like%20other%20places.%20We%20don't%20have%20hurricanes%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20wildfires%2C%20we%20have%20the%20occasional%20tornado%2C%20but%20that's%20super%20rare%20in%20the%20actual%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we've%20been%20super%20insulated%20from%20all%20these%20crazy%20highs%20and%20lows%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20big%20cities%20have%20seen%2C%20especially%20over%20the%20past%20five%2C%20six%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20%26quot%3BSan%20Francisco%2C%20or%20really%20any%20California%20town%2C%20saw%2040%25%2C%2050%25%20appreciation%20%E2%80%94%20these%20crazy%20jumps%20on%20these%20properties%20%E2%80%94%20so%20that%20when%20interest%20rates%20went%20up%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20they%20also%20saw%2040%25%2C%2050%25%20drops%20in%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20Hart%20explained.%20Louisville%2C%20which%20he%20said%20saw%20appreciation%20between%2010%25%20and%2014%25%20in%20that%20same%20timeframe%2C%20didn't%20have%20that%20issue.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20been%20super%20steady%20so%20no%20one's%20having%20to%20jump%20all%20around%20for%20crazy%20deals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20could%20change%2C%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20other%20markets%20in%20the%20south%20that%20are%20booming%3A%20%26quot%3BAustin's%20insane%2C%20Nashville's%20insane.%20Louisville%20has%20stayed%20pretty%20steady%2C%20but%20it%20might%20turn%20into%20that%20one%20day.%20We%20got%20a%20Topgolf%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20we've%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20infrastructure%20changes%2C%20so%20maybe%20we'll%20get%20super%20popular%20like%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20at%20this%20point%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20good%20place%20to%20live%2C%20and%20you%20can%20still%20buy%20a%20house%20for%20under%20%24250%2C000.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investors-factors-to-consider-when-choosing-market-city-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insi