0two%20days%20after%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20noose%20around%20his%20neck%2C%20Sharma%20recorded%20a%20nearly%20seven-minute%20harrowing%20video%20in%20which%20he%20accused%20his%20wife%20of%20being%20involved%20with%20another%20man%20romantically.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20for%20authorities.%20The%20law%20needs%20to%20protect%20men%2C%20or%20there%20will%20be%20a%20time%20when%20there%20will%20be%20no%20men%20left%20to%20blame.%20My%20wife%20was%20involved%20with%20another%20man...But%20what%20can%20I%20do%3F%20It%20does%20not%20matter%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20paused%20for%20a%20while%2C%20then%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20dying.%20I%20want%20to%20go.%20Please%20think%20about%20men.%20I'm%20sorry%2C%20everyone.%20Please%2C%20someone%20should%20talk%20about%20men.%20They%20become%20very%20lonely.%20Everything%20will%20get%20better%20once%20I%20go.%20I%20have%20attempted%20suicide%20even%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20clip%20was%20released%2C%20the%20techie's%20wife%2C%20Nikita%2C%20made%20a%20counter-video%20in%20which%20she%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20accused%20her%20husband%20of%20beating%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20day%20he%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20he%20had%20dropped%20me%20at%20my%20maternal%20home.%20Whatever%20claims%20he%20has%20made%20about%20me%2C%20it%20is%20about%20my%20past.%20It%20is%20not%20related%20to%20anything%20after%20our%20marriage.%20He%20has%20tried%20to%20harm%20himself%20multiple%20times%20before...I%20have%20stopped%20him%20at%20least%20three%20times.%20He%20used%20to%20drink%20and%20beat%20me%20up%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20techie's%20wife%20also%20claimed%20that%20she%20had%20informed%20his%20parents%20about%20him%20trying%20to%20harm%20himself%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20do%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20told%20his%20parents%20everything%2