ichael%20Cuggino's%20fund%20outperformed%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20gaining%2028%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPAGRX's%20success%20is%20due%20to%20its%20unique%20strategy%2C%20he%20says%2C%20focusing%20on%20quality%20growth%20firms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20fund%20screens%20stocks%20for%20factors%20including%20strong%20pricing%20power%2C%20earnings%20growth%2C%20and%20valuation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Cuggino%2C%20manager%20of%20the%20Permanent%20Portfolio%20Aggressive%20Growth%20Portfolio%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Ffunds%2Fpermanent-portfolio-aggressive-growth-portfolio-class-i-us7141993045%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPAGRX%3C%2Fa%3E)%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Finvestor-of-the-month%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI's%20Investor%20of%20the%20Month%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20fund%20has%20slipped%20over%20the%20last%20week%20as%20the%20market%20has%20faced%20a%20few%20macroeconomic%20challenges%2C%20it%20was%20off%20to%20a%20hot%20start%20in%20February%2C%20rising%209.5%25%20through%20the%2018th.%20And%20on%20a%20trailing%2012-month%20basis%2C%20it's%20smashing%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20returning%2028%25%20versus%20the%20index's%2017%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20par%20for%20the%20course%20for%20Cuggino's%20fund.%20Gaining%20an%20average%20of%2013.28%25%20a%20year%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20he's%20outperformed%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20annualized%2013.1%25%20returns%20over%20that%20time.%20Last%20year%2C%20Cuggino%20notched%20a%2044%25%20gain%20versus%20the%20benchmark's%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20has%20he%20generated%20the%20impressive%20alpha%3F%20Cuggino%20attributes%20his%20success%20to%20the%20independent%20nature%20of%20the%20fund.%20It%20doesn't%20set%20out%20to%20track%20particular%20indexes%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20look%20to%20invest%20along%20any%20particular%20theme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20managers%20will%20look%20at%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20ratings%20and%20go%2C%20'Well%2C%20transports%20are%206%25%2C%20so%20I'm%20gonna%20go%20to%207%25%20transports%20or%203%25.%20We%20don't%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20kind%20of%20throw%20those%20weightings%20out%20and%20do%20our%20own.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it%20simply%20seeks%20to%20identify%20quality%20growth%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20this%2C%20Cuggino%20said%2C%20by%20screening%20for%20firms%20with%20strong%20pricing%20power%2C%20earnings%20growth%2C%20revenue%20growth%2C%20who%20their%20management%20team%20is%2C%20what%20their%20total%20addressable%20market%20is%2C%20and%20whether%20or%20not%20its%20valuation%20sits%20at%20a%20reasonable%20level%20relative%20to%20other%20stocks%20in%20its%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20formula%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20high%20level%20of%20exposure%20to%20the%20tech%20sector%20at%2038%25%20of%20the%20fund%2C%20but%20also%20in%20stocks%20across%20several%20sectors.%20So%20while%20PAGRX's%20performance%20has%20been%20in%20part%20due%20to%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20tech%20giants%20leading%20the%20market%2C%20it's%20also%20gotten%20help%20from%20a%20smattering%20of%20different%20sectors%2C%20including%20industrials%2C%20consumer%20cyclicals%2C%20and%20communication%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20the%20fund's%20top%2010%20holdings%2C%20their%20performance%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months%2C%20and%20their%20weightings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia%3A%2067%25%20returns%20LTM%3B%2012.48%25%20weighting%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPalantir%3A%20279%25%20returns%20LTM%3B%2010.7%25%20weighting%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBroadcom%3A%2062.6%25%20returns%20LTM%3B%207.66%25%20weighting%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%3A%2039.8%25%20returns%20LTM%3B%205.97%25%20weighting%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFreeport-McMoran%3A%20-0.2%25%20returns%20LTM%3B%204.66%25%20weighting%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EParker-Hannifin%3A%2024.4%25%20returns%20LTM%3B%203.67%25%20weighting%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWilliams-Sonoma%3A%2072.6%25%20returns%20LTM%3B%203.66%25%20weighting%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECostco%3A%2038.4%25%20returns%20LTM%3B%203.39%25%20weighting%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAir%20Products%20%26amp%3B%20Chemicals%3A%2036.8%25%20returns%20LTM%3B%202.9%25%20weighting%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHF%20Sinclair%3A%20-40.8%25%20returns%20LTM%3B%202.5%25%20weighting%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20trade%20has%20given%20PAGRX%20a%20boost%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20and%20Cuggino%20sees%20it%20continuing%20to%20drive%20returns.%20But%20he%20also%20acknowledged%20that%20risks%20for%20a%20reversal%20in%20the%20rally%20are%20growing%20amid%20high%20valuations%20and%20geopolitical%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20longer%20you%20go%20without%20a%20correction%20or%20a%20consolidation%20makes%20one%20more%20likely%2C%20I%20think%2C%20at%20some%20point%20during%20the%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuggino%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20scenario%2C%20he'll%20be%20looking%20for%20energy%20and%20materials%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20slack%2C%20given%20their%20recent%20underperformance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you've%20got%20to%20be%20careful%2C%20and%20the%20way%20you%20be%20careful%20is%20invest%20in%20areas%20that%20maybe%20haven't%20kept%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20you're%20patient%2C%20you%20have%20some%20room%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuggino's%20fund%20has%20a%205.06%25%20weighting%20to%20the%20energy%20sector%20and%20a%2012.77%25%20weighting%20to%20materials.%20Funds%20like%20the%20iShares%20U.S.%20Basic%20Materials%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-us-basic-materials-etf-us4642878387%3FmiRedirects%3D2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIYM%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20the%20Vanguard%20Energy%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fvanguard-energy-index-fund-etf-shares-us92204a3068%3FmiRedirects%3D2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVDE%3C%2Fa%3E)%20offer%20broad%20exposure%20to%20these%20trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20considered%20for%20BI's%20Investor%20of%20the%20Month%20include%20managers%20of%20US-listed%20mutual%20funds%20or%20ETFs%2C%20those%20whose%20funds%20have%20outperformed%20peers%20in%20a%20given%20month%2C%20and%20those%20whose%20funds%20are%20outperforming%20a%20benchmark%20index%20(in%20most%20cases%20this%20will%20be%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500)%20on%20a%20trailing%2012-month%20basis.%20Leveraged%20funds%20are%20not%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ab49814-cc82-4205-b6b2-e58144b67b93%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYear-to-date%20leaderboard%20(as%20of%20market%20close%20on%20February%2026)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EQuantified%20Evolution%20Plus%20Fund%20Investor%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D29ad2167ea0f8e4ae5735f2cafb18adba5257d8dc6e38becf856e5fbf0f057e7%26postID%3D67bcb9540060db112e239322%26postSlug%3Dinvestor-of-the-month-top-fund-managers-beat-sp500-cuggino-2025-2%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.morningstar.com%252Ffunds%252Fxnas%252Fqevox%252Fquote%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQEVOX%3C%2Fa%3E)%3A%2011.68%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIndependent%20Franchise%20Partners%20US%20Equity%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Ffunds%2Findependent-franchise-partners-us-equity-fund-us00770g1022%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIFPUX%3C%2Fa%3E)%3A%2011.3%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKinetics%20Paradigm%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Ffunds%2Fkinetics-paradigm-fund-no-load-class-us4946136078%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWWNPX%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E)%3A%2010.94%25%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStrategy%20Shares%20Gold%20Enhanced%20Yield%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20hr