fter%20former%20Syrian%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsyria-bashar-al-assad-assad-family-damascus-the-al-assads-syrias-first-familys-rapid-rise-brutal-rule-abrupt-end-7198899%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBashar%20al-Assad%3C%2Fa%3E's%20downfall%20and%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20an%20uncertain%20future%20of%20the%20country's%20new%20leadership%20under%20interim%20President%20Ahmad%20al-Sharaa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Exclusive%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsyria-bashar-al-assad-damascus-ndtv-exclusive-repression-torture-slavery-syrians-recall-horrors-of-assad-rule-7361958%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERepression%2C%20Torture%2C%20Slavery%20-%20Syrians%20Recall%20Horrors%20Of%20Assad%20Rule%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20Druze%20community%2C%20not%20much%20has%20changed.%20Since%202015%2C%20Suwayda%20was%20under%20cautious%20control%20of%20the%20Assad%20regime.%20The%20state%20institutions%20functioned%2C%20but%20security%20was%20limited.%20After%20Assad's%20fall%2C%20the%20situation%20remained%20largely%20the%20same%2C%20except%20that%20the%20poorest%20lost%20government%20support%20for%20bread%20and%20essential%20goods%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahmed%20Al%20Shareef%2C%20a%20Druze%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20Syria%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20council%2C%20according%20to%20its%20statement%2C%20is%20tasked%20with%20safeguarding%20civilians%20and%20public%20property%2C%20coordinating%20with%20other%20security%20factions%2C%20and%20ensuring%20the%20region's%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomehow%2C%20safety%20improved%2C%20though%20the%20situation%20remains%20dangerous.%20Most%20of%20the%20gangs%20and%20cartels%20in%20Suwayda%20were%20backed%20by%20Assad%2C%20and%20when%20he%20fell%2C%20they%20collapsed%20too.%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS)%20-%20headed%20by%20al-Sharaa%20-%20hasn't%20fully%20entered%20Suwayda%20because%20the%20people%20reject%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Al%20Shareef%2C%2036%2C%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BDruze%20in%20Syria%20are%20not%20only%20in%20Suwayda.%20There%20are%20small%20Druze%20communities%20in%20Idlib%2C%20Quneitra%2C%20and%20western%20rural%20Damascus.%20Some%20Druze%20in%20Idlib%20were%20forced%20to%20convert%20to%20Islam%20under%20the%20Al-Nusra%20Front%20-%20HTS'%20precursor%20-%20over%20a%20ten-year%20period.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Long-Brewing%20Movement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Suwayda%20Military%20Council%20originally%20emerged%20as%20the%20Interim%20Military%20Council%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20shortly%20after%20Assad's%20government%20fell.%20Its%20formation%20was%20a%20response%20to%20deteriorating%20security%20conditions%20following%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Syrian%20Arab%20Army%20(SAA)%20forces%20from%20the%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20council's%20commander%2C%20a%20man%20named%20Tareq%20Al%20Shoufi%2C%20in%20his%20first%20public%20remarks%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Druze%20body%20seeks%20to%20integrate%20into%20a%20unified%20Syrian%20army%2C%20promoting%20secularism%2C%20democracy%2C%20and%20decentralisation%20as%20foundational%20principles%20for%20justice%20and%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20Druze%20leaders%20welcomed%20the%20initiative.%20Syria's%20Druze%20spiritual%20leader%2C%20Sheikh%20Hikmat%20al-Hajri%20has%20rejected%20the%20council%2C%20accusing%20its%20members%20of%20separatism%20and%20insisting%20they%20do%20not%20represent%20the%20Druze%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Exclusive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsyria-bashar-al-assad-damascus-ndtv-exclusive-ground-report-on-assad-free-syria-what-future-looks-like-7230209%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlimpse%20Of%20An%20Assad-Free%20Syria%2C%20What%20The%20Future%20Looks%20Like%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20groups%20aligned%20with%20the%20SDF%2C%20Israel%2C%20or%20the%20US%20are%20ambiguous%2C%20like%20the%20Free%20Syrian%20Army%2C%20which%20disappeared%20for%20ten%20years%20before%20reappearing%20the%20night%20Assad%20fell%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Al%20Shareef%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyria's%20interim%20President%20Ahmad%20al-Sharaa%2C%20also%20known%20by%20the%20nom%20de%20guerre%20Abu%20Mohammad%20al-Julani%2C%20has%20met%20with%20a%20delegation%20from%20Suwayda%20to%20discuss%20security%20concerns%2C%20political%20participation%2C%20and%20economic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20have%20been%20apprehensions%20within%20the%20community%20considering%20al-Sharaa's%20past%20as%20leader%20of%20HTS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Suwayda%2C%20Islamists%20can%20never%20impose%20Islamic%20law%20in%20a%20region%20that%20is%2090%20per%20cent%20Druze.%20Still%2C%20the%20general%20perception%20of%20al-Sharaa%20is%20worsening%20because%20he%20hasn't%20shown%20seriousness%20in%20building%20a%20state.%20Transparency%20is%20nonexistent%20-%20no%20formal%20declarations%2C%20just%20militia%20leaders%20declaring%20him%20president%20in%20a%20Telegram%20group.%20His%20latest%20speech%20presented%20him%20as%20a%20strongman%2C%20implying%20he%20will%20use%20force%20to%20impose%20his%20political%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Al%20Shareef%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Symbol%20of%20Resistance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Suwayda%20Military%20Council%20has%20adopted%20a%20flag%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20used%20by%20the%20Kurdish-led%20Syrian%20Democratic%20Forces%20(SDF).%20However%2C%20this%20version%20features%20Suwayda%20Governorate%20with%20the%20Druze%20five-pointed%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20council%20has%20expressed%20openness%20to%20cooperating%20with%20the%20SDF%2C%20acknowledging%20their%20shared%20struggle%20against%20terrorism%20and%20dictatorship.%20Since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw