20obtaining%20their%20license%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20turned%2018%2C%20or%20pausing%20college%20studies%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20described%20themselves%20as%20especially%20entrepreneurial%20and%20seeking%20an%20alternative%20to%20a%20typical%20desk%20job%20%E2%80%94%20and%20said%20they%20found%20the%20work%20rewarding%2C%20both%20on%20a%20financial%20and%20a%20personal%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarios%20Milonas%2C%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20based%20in%20New%20York%2C%20started%20in%20the%20business%20when%20he%20was%2019%20and%20looking%20for%20direction%20in%20his%20career.%20He%20wanted%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20a%20regular%209-to-5%2C%20and%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20steer%20clear%20of%20student%20loans%2C%20was%20taking%20classes%20at%20his%20local%20community%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20felt%20like%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20able%20to%20experience%20financial%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20shied%20away%20from%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20forced%20into%20a%20job%20just%20to%20pay%20of%20student%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Marios%20Milonas%20on%20a%20gray%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bcc1664e7cbbbe3dc45c01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22263%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarios%20Milonas%20said%20he%20began%20working%20on%20his%20real%20estate%20license%20when%20he%20was%2019.%20It%20took%20him%20more%20than%20a%20year%20to%20sell%20his%20first%20home%2C%20he%20told%20BI.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Marios%20Milonas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20girlfriend's%20father%2C%20who%20had%20worked%20in%20real%20estate%20for%20more%20than%2020%20years%2C%20recommended%20he%20try%20it%20out.%20After%20a%20few%20weeks%20of%20coursework%2C%20he%20got%20his%20license%20and%20soon%20after%20dropped%20out%20of%20community%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20was%20tough%2C%20at%20first.%20Milanos%20didn't%20sell%20a%20single%20home%20for%20his%20first%20year%20in%20the%20business%2C%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20%26quot%3Bbaby%20face%26quot%3B%20also%20held%20him%20back%2C%20he%20said%2C%20recalling%20offhand%20comments%20from%20other%20professionals%20in%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20person%20came%20in%20and%20said%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20thought%20you%20were%2013%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20Milanos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20began%20to%20subside%20as%20he%20began%20to%20grow%20more%20confident%20and%20worked%20on%20appearing%20more%20knowledgeable%20in%20front%20of%20his%20clients.%20Once%20the%20housing%20market%20began%20to%20heat%20back%20up%2C%20he%20felt%20things%20finally%20coming%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20that%20housing%20market%20opened%20up%2C%20it%20was%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20began%20making%20a%20six-figure%20salary%20when%20he%20was%2021%20years%20old.%20Milonas%20made%20over%20%24300%2C000%20in%20commission%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20financial%20statements%20viewed%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChloe%20De%20Verrier%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20realtor%20based%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20also%20began%20working%20on%20getting%20her%20real%20estate%20license%20when%20she%20was%2019.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%20attending%20UCLA%20and%20felt%20unsure%20about%20her%20career%20path.%20She%20did%2C%20though%2C%20know%20that%20she%20wanted%20to%20run%20her%20own%20business%2C%20and%20have%20full%20control%20over%20her%20schedule.%20Real%20estate%20seemed%20like%20the%20right%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20kind%20of%20having%20that%2C%20I%20guess%2C%20quarter-life%20crisis%20of%2C%20'I%20don't%20know%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20kind%20of%20just%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20of%20faith.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20temporarily%20drop%20out%20of%20college%20and%20pursue%20real%20estate%20full-time.%20Her%20first%20official%20day%20in%20business%20was%20her%2021st%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222652%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chloe%20De%20Verrier%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bcc18dc040bd1b4ca2f98e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221326%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDe%20Verrier%20said%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20restaurant%20hostess%20on%20the%20side%20while%20she%20was%20first%20trying%20her%20hand%20at%20being%20a%20real%20estate%20agent.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Chloe%20De%20Verrier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20took%20De%20Verrier%20eight%20months%20to%20sell%20her%20first%20home%2C%20which%20she%20attributes%20to%20the%20pandemic%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20was%20just%20starting%20out%20in%20the%20industry.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20she%20lived%20off%20her%20savings%20and%20moonlighted%20as%20a%20restaurant%20hostess%20for%20extra%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20a%20complete%20shit%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20do%20real%20estate%20all%20day%20during%20the%20day%2C%20go%20to%20my%20night%20shift.%20And%20it%20would%20be%20funny%20because%20clients%20would%20call%20me%20when%20I%20was%20on%20shift%2C%20and%20so%20I%20would%20make%20some%20excuse%20to%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%20or%20step%20into%20the%20alleyway%20to%20negotiate%20deals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20times%2C%20she%20also%20doubted%20herself%20because%20of%20her%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho's%20going%20to%20trust%20a%2020-something-year-old%20to%20buy%20or%20sell%20their%20biggest%20asset%3F%26quot%3B%20De%20Verrier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20people%20don't%20seem%20to%20care%20about%20how%20young%20she%20was.%20De%20Verrier%20says%20clients%20typically%20trust%20her%20because%20she's%20knowledgeable%20and%20does%20her%20best%20to%20come%20across%20as%20professional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20this%20day%2C%20people%20are%20like%2C%20you%20look%2023%2C%20but%20you%20act%20%5Bolder%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BLooking%20back%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20was%20as%20big%20of%20a%20deal%20as%20I%20made%20it%20out%20to%20be%20in%20my%20head.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDe%20Verrier%20made%20over%20%24100%2C000%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20viewed%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Khateri%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20real-estate%20agent%20in%20Virginia%2C%20said%20he%20got%20his%20real%20estate%20license%20when%20he%20was%2018%2C%20but%20he%20was%20dabbling%20in%20real%20estate%20long%20before%20that.%20Khateri%20helped%20his%20immigrant%20parents%20read%20documents%20and%20sell%20their%20home%20twice%20when%20he%20was%20younger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223888%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Joseph%20Khateri%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b8a4adeb4be2fff9a53d38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKhateri%2C%20who%20also%20works%20full-time%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%2C%20said%20he%20expected%20to%20make%20around%20%24200%2C000%20in%20combined%20income%20in%202025.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Joseph%20Khateri%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20Khateri%20helped%20his%20parents%20move%2C%20the%20realtor%20who%20sold%20them%20their%20house%20in%20Virginia%20told%20him%20to%20think%20about%20getting%20into%20the%20real%20estate%20business.%20Afer%20obtaining%20his%20license%2C%20he%20plunged%20into%20the%20real%20estate%20business%20full-time%2C%20working%20as%20many%20as%2080%20hours%20a%20week%20his%20first%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhateri%20described%20his%20approach%20to%20real-estate%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20game%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20worked%20doggedly%20to%20bring%20up%20his%20hourly%20rate%2C%20or%20what%20his%20salary%20would%20be%20if%20he%20were%20paid%20by%20the%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20tough%20going%2C%20though.%20It%20took%20Khateri%20around%20six%20months%20to%20sell%20his%20first%20home.%20His%20commission%2C%20when%20subtracting%20fees%20from%20his%20brokerage%20and%20other%20work-related%20expenses%2C%20came%20out%20to%20a%20rate%20of%20around%20%242%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20losing%20money%20every%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20were%20like%2C%20'Joseph%2C%20what%20are%20you%20doing%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20too%2C%20said%20he%20had%20trouble%20doing%20deals%20because%20of%20his%20age.%20%26quot%3BAgeism%20is%20a%20very%20big%20thing%20with%20real%20estate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20things%20have%20picked%20up.%20Last%20year%2C%20Khateri%20made%20around%20%2470%2C000%20from%20his%20real%20estate%20business%20alone%2C%20which%20includes%20his%20income%20from%20commission%2C%20referrals%20to%20clients%2C%20and%20consulting%2C%20statements%20viewed%20by%20BI%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gen%20Z%20realtors%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20said%20they%20all%20want%20to%20stick%20with%20real%20estate%2C%20even%20if%20its%20just%20as%20a%20side%20hustle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilonas%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20working-class%20family%20in%20Queens%2C%20said%20he%20planned%20on%20scaling%20his%20business%20and%20building%20generational%20wealth%20through%20his%20real%20estate%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhateri%20picked%20up%20a%20full-time%20job%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20last%20year%20and%20said%20he%20would%20continue%20to%20work%20in%20real%20estate%20on%20the%20side.%20Money%20is%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20why%2C%20he%20admits%2C%20as%20he's%20a%20close%20follower%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ffinancial-independence-retire-early%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Independence%2C%20