Unused%26quot%3B%3A%20CAG%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20review%20of%20the%20medical%20infrastructure%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fdelhi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20indicates%20under-utilisation%20of%20funds%20provided%20by%20the%20centre%20during%20the%20COVID%20crisis%2C%20a%20severe%20shortage%20of%20staff%2C%20and%20long%20waiting%20times%20for%20major%20surgeries%2C%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor-General%20said%20in%20a%20report%20tabled%20in%20the%20Assembly%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seven-page%20CAG%20report%20-%20one%20of%20over%20a%20dozen%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20has%20vowed%20to%20present%20in%20the%20House%2C%20as%20proof%20of%20corruption%20by%20predecessors%20AAP%20-%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20%26quot%3Bdire%20condition%26quot%3B%20of%20'%3Cem%3Emohalla%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20or%20neighbourhood%2C%20clinics%2C%20which%20were%20a%20flagship%20measure%20of%20the%20earlier%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20slammed%20these%20and%20other%20failings%20-%20such%20as%20not%20having%20enough%20doctors%20and%20nurses%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20funding%20for%20maternal%20health%20programmes%2C%20ambulances%20without%20key%20equipment%2C%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20ICUs%20-%20as%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20inaction%20towards%20a%20severe%20shortage%20of%20medical%20infrastructure...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Does%20CAG%20Report%20Say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20begins%20by%20stating%20the%20AAP%20government%20used%20Rs%20582.84%20of%20the%20Rs%20787.91%20crore%20released%20by%20the%20centre%20during%20the%20COVID%20pandemic.%20The%20unused%20amount%20included%20Rs%2030.52%20crore%20for%20human%20resources%2C%20indicating%20'under-payment%20to%2C%20and%20lower%20deployment%20of%2C%20staff'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20additional%20Rs%20119.95%20crore%20had%20been%20released%20for%20medicines%20and%20medical%20supplies%2C%20including%20PPE%2C%20or%20personal%20protective%20equipment%2C%20which%20was%20a%20critical%20requirement%20for%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20treating%20COVID%20patients.%20A%20widespread%20shortage%20of%20PPEs%20was%20reported%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20this%20amount%20only%20Rs%2083.14%20crore%20was%20used%2C%20the%20CAG%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Not%20Enough%20Beds%2C%20Staff'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20the%20AAP%20government%20failed%20to%20utilise%20the%20budget%20to%20increase%20hospital%20beds%3B%20from%202016%2F17%20to%202020%2F21%20budget%20provisions%20were%20made%20for%2032%2C000%20but%20only%201%2C357%20were%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOccupancy%20was%20between%20a%20staggering%20101%20per%20cent%20and%20189%20per%20cent%2C%20the%20CAG%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20beds%20was%20matched%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20shortage%20of%20manpower%20in%20the%20public%20health%20sector%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20claiming%20a%20shortfall%20of%20over%202%2C000%20staff%20between%20five%20institutions%20alone%2C%20including%20the%20Lok%20Nayak%20Hospital%2C%20and%20the%20Chacha%20Nehru%20Bal%20Chikitsalaya%2C%20a%20pediatric%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20two%20others%20-%20the%20Janakpuri%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Super%20Speciality%20Hospitals%20-%20there%20is%20a%2050%20per%20cent%20shortage%20of%20doctors%2C%2073%20per%20cent%20nursing%20staff%2C%20and%20at%20least%2017%20per%20cent%20paramedics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20non-availability%20of%20specialist%20doctors%20at%20the%20trauma%20centre%20in%20Lok%20Nayak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Waiting%20Times%20For%20Surgeries'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatients%20requiring%20major%20surgery-%20specifically%20relating%20to%20burn%20injuries%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20at%20least%20six%20months%20at%20Lok%20Nayak.%20Patients%20at%20Chacha%20Nehru%20Bal%20Chikitsalaya%20have%20to%20wait%20for%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELinked%20to%20that%2C%20the%20CAG%20report%20said%20also%2014%20of%2027%20hospitals%20audited%20did%20not%20have%20an%20ICU%2C%20or%20intensive%20care%20unit%2C%2016%20did%20not%20have%20blood%20banks%2C%20and%2012%20did%20not%20have%20ambulances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20Toilets%20In%20Mohalla%20Clinics'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20was%20also%20critical%20of%20the%20earlier%20AAP%20government's%20flagship%20'%3Cem%3Emohalla%3C%2Fem%3E'%20clinics%20initiative%2C%20saying%2021%20did%20not%20have%20bathrooms%2C%2015%20had%20no%20power%20back-up%2C%20and%2012%20were%20not%20disabled-friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20vs%20AAP%20On%20Auditors'%20Reports%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20presented%20post%202%20pm%2C%20and%20there%20will%20almost%20certainly%20be%20chaos%20in%20the%20House%20as%20the%20under-fire%20AAP%20MLAs%20respond.%20The%20opening%20days%20of%20this%20Assembly%20session%20-%20the%20first%20after%20the%20BJP's%20thumping%20win%20in%20the%20election%20this%20month%20-%20have%20already%20see%20pitched%20battles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finjustice-to-opposition-atishi-writes-to-speaker-on-aap-mlas-suspension-7813740%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll_Imagetopscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BInjustice%20To%20Opposition%26quot%3B%3A%20Atishi%20On%20AAP%20MLAs'%20Suspension%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20session%20today%2C%20AAP%20leaders%20sat%20outside%20the%20Assembly%20to%20protest%20the%20suspension%20of%2021%20lawmakers%20earlier%20this%20week.%20Ex-Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%2C%20now%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20wrote%20to%20Speaker%20Vijender%20Gupta%20to%20flag%20the%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20blow%20to%20democratic%20values%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C