under%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20I%20got%20information%20about%20the%20inhuman%20act%20done%20with%20our%20innocent%20daughter%20in%20Dinara%20of%20Shivpuri%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20the%20family%20members%20on%20the%20phone%20today%20and%20encouraged%20them.%20My%20daughter%20is%20currently%20admitted%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20her%20condition%20is%20stable.%20I%20am%20constantly%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20team%20of%20doctors.%20There%20is%20no%20place%20for%20such%20crimes%20in%20our%20region%20and%20state.%20I%20took%20immediate%20cognizance%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20spoke%20to%20the%20district%20administration%20and%20Shivpuri%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20and%20directed%20them%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20against%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Scindia%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A5%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%83%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%9C%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AB%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%9A%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%8C%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B2