om%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fat-least-47-feared-trapped-after-glacier-burst-in-indian-himalayas-13318521%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fat-least-47-feared-trapped-after-glacier-burst-in-indian-himalayas-13318521%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BArbitrary%2C%20Illegal%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20Sets%20Aside%20Dismissal%20Of%202%20Women%20Civil%20Judges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20set%20aside%20the%20orders%20the%20dismissal%20of%20two%20women%20civil%20judges%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%202023%2C%20terming%20the%20action%20as%20%26quot%3Bpunitive%2C%20arbitrary%20and%20illegal%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20pertained%20to%20the%20dismissal%20of%20Judges%20Aditi%20Kumar%20Sharma%20and%20Sarita%20Chaudhary%2C%20who%20had%20joined%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20judicial%20service%20in%202018%20and%202017%20respectively.%20A%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20N%20Kotiswar%20Singh%20noted%20that%20one%20of%20judges%2C%20during%20probation%20period%2C%20had%20got%20married%2C%20contracted%20Covid-19%2C%20had%20a%20miscarriage%2C%20and%20her%20brother%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20there%20is%20birth%20there%20is%20sense%20of%20fulfillment%20whereas%20miscarriage%20has%20serious%20effect%20on%20mental%20health%20of%20women%20which%20has%20psychological%20impact%20which%20even%20leads%20to%20suicide%20and%20recurring%20miscarriages%20even%20has%20severe%20effects%20on%20health.%20Miscarriage%20affects%20a%20person's%20identity%2C%20stigma%2C%20isolation%20in%20other%20factors.%20It%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20find%20comfort%20in%20growing%20number%20of%20women%20judicial%20officers%20unless%20we%20secure%20a%20comfortable%20atmosphere%20for%20them%20to%20work%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Nagarathana%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20adding%20that%20women%20judges%20often%20take%20pain-killer%20medicines%20to%20sit%20through%20the%20entire%20day%20in%20court%20on%20certain%20days%2C%20the%20Bench%20added%20that%20freedom%20from%20discrimination%20for%20women%20during%20pregnancy%20is%20precious%20right.%20The%20top%20court%20direct%20the%20reinstatement%20of%20both%20women%20judges%20within%2015%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%20said%20a%20report%20given%20by%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20was%20also%20not%20satisfactory%20in%20persuading%20the%20Bench%20to%20take%20a%20different%20view.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hold%20that%20the%20termination%20was%20in%20the%20form%20of%20punishment.%20The%20termination%20was%20stigmatic%20in%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2011%2C%202023%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20taken%20a%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20of%20the%20termination%20of%20six%20women%20civil%20judges%20by%20the%20state%20government%20over%20their%20alleged%20unsatisfactory%20performance.%20However%2C%20a%20full%20court%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20reconsidered%20its%20earlier%20resolutions%20on%20August%201%2C%202024%20and%20decided%20to%20reinstate%20four%20officers--%20Jyoti%20Varkade%2C%20Sushri%20Sonakshi%20Joshi%2C%20Sushri%20Priya%20Sharma%20and%20Rachna%20Atulkar%20Joshi%20--%20on%20certain%20terms%20and%20conditions%2C%20leaving%20out%20the%20other%20two%2C%20Aditi%20Kumar%20Sharma%20and%20Sarita%20Chaudhary%20from%20the%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2017%2C%202024%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20reserved%20its%20verdict%20in%20the%20matter%20pertaining%20to%20the%20termination%20of%20two%20women%20judicial%20officers%20by%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740731640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqjntv49_supreme-court-_625x300_13_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farbitrary-illegal-top-court-sets-aside-dismissal-of-two-women-civil-judges-7814395%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%