%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bfe01869253ccddf97ba42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChris%20Hwang%20started%20The%20Golden%20Duck%20in%202015%20with%20his%20partner%2C%20Jonathan%20Shen.%3Cp%3EThe%20Golden%20Duck%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChris%20Hwang%2C%20cofounder%20of%20The%20Golden%20Duck%2C%20started%20the%20snack%20brand%20in%202015%20with%20one%20product%20%E2%80%94%20salted%20egg%20yolk%20chips.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20decade%20on%2C%20it's%20sold%20in%20over%203%2C000%20stores%20and%20plans%20to%20expand%20into%20the%20US%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFrom%20selling%20off%20his%20cars%20to%20afford%20payroll%20in%20the%20pandemic%2C%20here's%20how%20he%20built%20the%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Chris%20Hwang%2C%20the%2033-year-old%20cofounder%20of%20The%20Golden%20Duck%2C%20a%20Singaporean%20snack%20brand.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2023%2C%20I%20dropped%20out%20of%20law%20school%20to%20start%20The%C2%A0Golden%20Duck%2C%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20gourmet%20snack%20brand%20that%20reimagines%20Asian%20flavors%20like%20salted%20egg%20yolk%3B%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20it%20is%20sold%20in%20over%203%2C000%20stores%20worldwide.%20We've%20set%20our%20sights%20on%20expanding%20into%20the%20US%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20any%20culinary%20experience%2C%20but%20I%20love%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20for%20the%20brand%20came%20about%20when%20my%20cofounder%2C%20Jonathan%2C%20approached%20me%20one%20day%20and%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20think%20about%20salted%20egg%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BSalted%20egg%20is%20great.%20I%20love%20it%20in%20a%20Chinese%20Zi%20Char%20restaurant.%20I%20love%20salted%20egg%20crab.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20had%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20about%20we%20make%20salted%20egg%20yolk%20potato%20chips%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20the%20kind%20of%20chips%20that%20come%20with%20dips%2C%20a%20Western%20concept%20that%20doesn't%20really%20sell%20well%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHear%20me%20out.%20I%20found%20a%20way%20to%20put%20it%20on%20a%20chip%20in%20a%20dry%20format.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20and%20a%20chef%20friend%20of%20ours%2C%20and%20I%20tried%20it.%20It%20was%20so%20mind-blowingly%20good.%20The%20flavor%2C%20with%20the%20chilies%20and%20curry%20leaves%2C%20perfectly%20coated%20the%20chips.%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20do%20this%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f4b3baab-7314-435d-8cd6-f81d8d16bb66%5C%22%3ECooking%20out%20of%20one%20tiny%20kitchen%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20launched%20in%202015%20with%20just%20one%20product%20%E2%80%94%20salted%20egg%20yolk%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%2C%20our%20capacity%20was%20so%20limited%20that%20we%20were%20just%20making%20it%20out%20of%20a%20home%20kitchen%2C%20producing%20only%20about%2050%20packs%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20selling%20them%20at%20a%20tiny%20seven-foot-long%20pop-up%20booth%20in%20Singapore's%20Suntec%20City%20mall%20for%20%247%20a%20pop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20first%20day%2C%20the%20sales%20were%20not%20too%20crazy.%20But%20on%20day%20two%2C%20a%20queue%20started%20forming.%20By%20day%20three%2C%20we%20had%20sold%20out%20by%203%20p.m.%20and%20had%20to%20put%20a%20maximum%20order%20of%20five%20packs%20per%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20products%20are%20often%20given%20as%20gifts%20or%20bought%20as%20souvenirs%2C%20and%20I%20think%20this%20is%20where%20it%20started.%20People%20started%20bringing%20their%20friends%20down%20to%20help%20them%20buy%20more%20packs%2C%20and%20it%20became%20a%20gift%20item%20for%20friends%20and%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0f59dd4-e300-40fb-ad23-a8d8a7407020%5C%22%3EA%20huge%20opportunity%20for%20authentic%20flavors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Golden%20Duck's%20two%20product%20lines%20%E2%80%94%20its%20snackboxes%20and%20canister%20chips.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ab1249eb4be2fff9a433ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Golden%20Duck%20sells%20snack%20boxes%20and%20canister%20chips.%3Cp%3EThe%20Golden%20Duck%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20have%20two%20lines%20of%20products%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eour%20snack%20boxes%2C%20which%20comprise%20flavors%20like%20salted%20egg%20crab%20seaweed%20tempura%20and%20salted%20egg%20fish%20skin%20chips%2C%20and%20a%20line%20of%20canister%20potato%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsian%20flavors%20are%20gaining%20traction%20in%20the%20West%2C%20and%20I%20think%20people%20all%20around%20the%20world%20are%20craving%20authentic%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20know%20what%20sour%20cream%20and%20onion%20flavor%20or%20barbecue%20tastes%20like.%20But%20why%20not%20have%20sour%20cream%20and%20Sriracha%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20of%20our%20newest%20flavors%20in%20the%20canister%20line%20of%20chips%20that%20we%20launched%20in%202024%2C%20along%20with%20others%20like%20truffle%20wagyu%20and%20Himalayan%20pink%20salt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f6888dec-72a8-41f3-b6bc-b4bbeb8bc25c%5C%22%3EChallenges%20in%20scaling%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20hesitant%20to%20scale%20up%20initially%2C%20scared%20that%20it%20was%20just%20a%20flash%20in%20the%20pan%20and%20it%20would%20flame%20out%20fast.%20So%20we%20were%20very%2C%20very%20hesitant%20to%20put%20in%20capital%20to%20set%20up%20a%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20pop-ups%20for%20a%20few%20months%20until%20we%20finally%20got%20a%20tiny%20store%20in%20Chinatown%2C%20which%20had%20just%20enough%20space%20for%20one%20person%20to%20work%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20we%20kept%20expanding.%20From%202016%20to%202018%2C%20we%20grew%20to%2010%20stores%20in%20Singapore%20and%20more%20stores%20overseas.%20At%20the%20peak%2C%20we%20had%20about%2015%20stores%2C%20and%20we%20were%20also%20selling%20to%20retailers%20like%207-Eleven%20and%20other%20supermarket%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20biggest%20surprises%20in%20our%20business%20came%20from%20scaling%20up%20our%20own%20manufacturing.%20The%20moment%20we%20tried%20to%20give%20a%20product%20a%20shelf%20life%2C%20we%20had%20to%20consider%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20will%20this%20taste%20after%20six%20months%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiring%20the%20right%20people%20was%20key.%20If%20you%20hire%20someone%20who%20hates%20being%20in%20a%20hot%20kitchen%2C%20your%20products%20will%20come%20out%20pretty%20bad.%20We%20needed%20to%20hire%20people%20who%20care%20about%20their%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f284a747-28ad-470d-b89b-33af9d6df81d%5C%22%3EWeathering%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lowest%20point%20in%20the%20business%20came%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20when%20our%20tourism%20revenue%20evaporated%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20subscribe%20to%20the%20ideology%20that%20leaders%20eat%20last.%20I%20thought%20%E2%80%94%20if%20the%20company%20can't%20afford%20payroll%20and%20cannot%20meet%20its%20obligations%20to%20continue%20its%20business%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20sell%20my%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%202019%20to%202021%2C%20I%20sold%20three%20cars%20so%20that%20I%20could%20lead%20the%20fundraising%20efforts%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20had%20to%20restructure%20the%20team%2C%20going%20from%20200%20head%20count%20to%20about%20120%20over%20the%20course%20of%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20tell%20friends%20that%20we'd%20brought%20on%20board%20that%20we%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20work%20together%20and%20that%20we%20were%20sorry%20for%20where%20the%20business%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20have%20a%20team%20of%2025%20people%2C%20producing%20results%20close%20to%20what%20our%20team%20of%20200%20was%20producing%20just%20five%20to%20six%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223224fb71-ddb8-42a3-867e-67e5325c40c3%5C%22%3EEyes%20set%20on%20a%20US%20expansion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20on%2C%20we%20now%20sell%20in%20countries%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20China%2C%20Australia%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20even%20Trinidad%20and%20Tobago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20we%20are%20eyeing%20the%20US%20as%20our%20new%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20returned%20from%20the%20US%20in%20December.%20It's%20a%20huge%20market%20for%20snacks%2C%20second%20to%20none.%20And%20the%20US%20consumer%20is%20so%20discerning%20and%20excited%2C%20and%20they're%20happy%20to%20consume%20and%20try%20new%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20wanted%20to%20develop%20something%20that%20they%20would%20find%20interesting%20and%20exciting%20but%20still%20familiar%2C%20so%20we%20didn't%20want%20to%20reinvent%20the%20wheel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20line%20of%20canister%20chips%20is%20basically%20like%20Pringles%20but%20better.%20It's%20so%20easy%20to%20explain%20to%20Americans%20because%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20tell%20them%20what%20fish%20skin%20is%20or%20what%20seaweed%20tempura%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-golden-duck-singaporean-snack-company-chris-hwang-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740712871000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bfe02e69253ccddf97ba47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-golden-duck-singaporean-snack-company-chris-hwang-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chris%20Hwang%2C%20cofounder%20of%20The%20Golden%20Duck%2C%20sold%20his%20cars%20to%20afford%20payroll%20in%20the%20pandemic.%20Here's%20how%2